race.description: Gorski Hardox Tough Tippers 5Th Grade F
race.comment: GREENER PASTURES (3) jumped well to win over the 520m at this track two runs back then prominent throughout when finishing second at this track last start. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Winning claims. SIMULATE (1) carved over from wide out and boxed on strongly to finish 1.5 lengths away in third (35.02) behind MOET MAGIC at this track. Goes well out of this box with a win and three minor placings. Expected to feature. MOET MAGIC (7) scored well last start as odds-on favourite by one length at this track in a handy 34.92 beating GATTLIN GLASS. Draws out wide but likes the trip. Recorded the quickest time on the card last start. Leading chance again.
